cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.PL 

This paper discusses the integration of reinforcement learning and symbolic planning to build intelligent autonomous agents. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with decision-making in a dynamic environment, which suggests the sub-category cs.RO (Robotics). The use of symbolic knowledge and plans indicates the sub-category cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper mentions the improvement of planning through learned experience, which falls under the sub-category cs.PL (Programming Languages).
